            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>An improved method for the reconstruction of diffused waveguide index profiles from experimental mode spectra is proposed. The method uses a parabolic approximation between successive points. It is tested on the example of an exponential profile, and applied to the reconstruction of index profiles in Ag<Superscript>+</Superscript> ion-exchanged waveguides from measured mode spectra. This method appears to work well also in the cases of very few mode wave-guides.</Para>
            </Abstract>
